---
title: Warm Bacon, Roasted Tomato and Lentil Salad with Aubergine and Croutons
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Warm Bacon, Roasted Tomato and Lentil Salad in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R17_W30_UK_QR2591-53_Main__8low-d1312d8c.jpg
